meta.title: Live Rugby API -  All Fixtures and Results for Castres
meta.description: Fixtures and Results for given team across all competitions, going back to beginning of our records. Note some matches will not have full match pages.

fields.id: Integer - unique fixture id, use to query match endpoint
fields.status: String - Not Started, First Half, Half Time, Second Half, Full Time, Postponed, Cancelled, Result
